类 mcfppBaseListener

java.lang.Object
top.alumopper.mcfpp.lib.mcfppBaseListener
所有已实现的接口:
org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener, mcfppListener
直接已知子类:
McfppImListener
public class mcfppBaseListener extends Object implements mcfppListener
This class provides an empty implementation of mcfppListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
